  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Speech intelligibility in noise will be evaluated in adults with moderate to moderate-severe&#xD;
      sensorineural hearing loss, using an assistive listening device and hearing aid, and compared&#xD;
      to speech intelligibility in noise using hearing aids alone.&#xD;
    </textblock>
